      <section class="section_faq7 color-scheme-4">
        <div class="padding-global">
          <div class="container-large">
            <div class="padding-section-large">
              <div class="faq7_component">
                <div class="margin-bottom margin-xxlarge">
                  <div class="text-align-center">
                    <div class="max-width-large align-center">
                      <h2 class="heading-style-h2 left">MMT Core Insights</h2>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="59f0a464-8771-a027-56b9-6530aadc4963" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">The Self-Financing State</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">A country like the UK, which has its own currency, never has to worry about running out of money. The government always creates new money when it spends, and that's how it pays for everything, not from taxes or by borrowing.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/self-financing-state" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="c730c73a-20dd-e83a-86f7-83281335e67b" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-23 text-weight-bold">The UK National Debt</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">UK debt represents money the government invested in our economy but hasn't taxed back. It corresponds exactly to the net financial savings held by the private sector; effectively, the government's liability is our asset.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/uk-national-debt" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="ccf24299-5f11-1911-5232-74c36621d05b" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-24 text-weight-bold">The Role of Taxation in the UK</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">The purpose of taxes is not to fund government spending; it is to create demand for the currency and to help manage the economy.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/role-of-taxation" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="9d6e7580-0ea2-3672-fa42-1bfee63e6107" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-25 text-weight-bold">Understanding UK Inflation</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">Inflation is defined as a sustained rise in the general price level. In the UK, inflation is not primarily caused by government spending creating "too much money" but by supply constraints, energy costs, and market power limiting how much the economy can actually produce.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/understanding-inflation" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="1c20c0ae-a8e9-f6bf-f612-e3ecb7dacfe7" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-25 text-weight-bold">The UK Government vs the Bond Market</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">The UK government cannot be forced into bankruptcy by rising bond yields because it creates the money required to pay bondholders.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/government-vs-bond-market" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="2d27e85b-1a6c-2b0a-d906-882c4bb0f0e2" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-25 text-weight-bold">How Money Actually Works: Step-by-Step</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">Once you understand that money is created by the state and that taxes create demand for it, the rest of how the economy works follows as a matter of pure logic.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/how-money-works" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <div id="but-what-about" class="padding-global">
        <div class="container-large">
          <div class="divider-horizontal page_divider"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="section_faq7 color-scheme-2">
        <div class="padding-global">
          <div class="container-large">
            <div class="padding-section-large">
              <div class="faq7_component">
                <div class="margin-bottom margin-xxlarge">
                  <div class="text-align-center">
                    <div class="max-width-large align-center">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small">
                        <h2 class="heading-style-h2 left">But what about...?</h2>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-size-medium approach">Common questions and misconceptions about Modern Monetary Theory</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-1" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">The National Debt is unsustainable</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">No, any nation that issues its own currency and has a floating exchange rate can always pay any bill presented in its own currency. This insight lies at the heart of MMT thinking. It is based on a precise understanding of what the UK national debt is â€“ and what it isn't.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/national-debt-unsustainable" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-4" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">Won't this cause inflation?</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">Inflation is caused by spending beyond the economy's productive capacity, not by government spending itself. MMT provides a framework for understanding when spending becomes inflationary and how to prevent it.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/wont-this-cause-inflation" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-5" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">It's just like a household budget</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">A currency-issuing government is fundamentally different from a household. Households must earn or borrow currency before they can spend. The UK government creates the currency that households and businesses use.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/household-budget" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-6" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">The markets will punish us</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">Bond markets do not control currency-issuing governments in the way commonly portrayed. The UK government can always meet its obligations in sterling. Market reactions reflect expectations about future policy, not genuine solvency concerns.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/markets-will-punish-us" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-7" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">It will destroy the currency</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">Exchange rates are influenced by many factors including trade balances, interest rate differentials, and investor sentiment. Government spending on productive capacity can strengthen rather than weaken a currency's long-term value.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/destroy-the-currency" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-8" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">What about Zimbabwe / Venezuela / Weimar Germany?</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">These cases involved political collapse, war, destruction of productive capacity, or loss of monetary sovereignty. They are not examples of normal fiscal policy causing hyperinflation.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/zimbabwe-venezuela-weimar" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-9" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">It's just communism / socialism</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">MMT is a description of how monetary systems actually operate, not a political ideology. It is compatible with a range of policy positions. Understanding the system accurately does not dictate what policies you should support.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/communism-socialism" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M6 3L11 8L6 13" stroke="CurrentColor" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                          </svg></div>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="accordion1_component">
                    <div data-w-id="objection-accordion-10" class="accordion1_top">
                      <div class="text-size-medium-22 text-weight-bold">No serious economist believes this</div>
                      <div class="accordion1_icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5303 20.8839C16.2374 21.1768 15.7626 21.1768 15.4697 20.8839L7.82318 13.2374C7.53029 12.9445 7.53029 12.4697 7.82318 12.1768L8.17674 11.8232C8.46963 11.5303 8.9445 11.5303 9.2374 11.8232L16 18.5858L22.7626 11.8232C23.0555 11.5303 23.5303 11.5303 23.8232 11.8232L24.1768 12.1768C24.4697 12.4697 24.4697 12.9445 24.1768 13.2374L16.5303 20.8839Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:0px" class="accordion1_bottom">
                      <div class="margin-bottom margin-small" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1rem;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">MMT builds on established traditions in monetary economics including Keynes, Minsky, Lerner, and institutional analysis of central banking. Its description of monetary operations aligns with how central bankers describe their own systems.</p>
                        <a href="/education/articles/no-serious-economist" class="button is-link is-icon w-inline-block" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                          <div>Read more</div>
                          <div class="icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed"><svg width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
